{"tid":334753,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[波台博士論文] 心理學角度研究 香港獌狗呢2星期既抗憤狀態成因","createTime":"2017-07-25T04:24:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T15:33:51.000Z","uid":54373,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1e1085410dc55f978906b1ea5d8c8031b5a198db","tid":334753,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T04:24:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">死獌狗,個個老母都係慰安婦,呢點大家都知<br />\n所以希望大家包容下獌狗,同佢地老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n死獌狗有幾多次來香港踢? 來左仲要坐唔爆,無氣氛<br />\n又出D支那仔董方卓唔專重比賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以香港獌狗只係一隻比主人遺棄的喪家犬<br />\n又期待佢地來香港,來到人又少,比賽質素又無<br />\n仲有隻送禮狗,既禮物都係比佢地拎來抹屎<br />\n心灰以冷,非常可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以今次香港死獌狗見到猁狗有氣氛,又多球星睇<br />\n即刻觸動神經,令佢地極度自卑<br />\n從而出現反社會,反人格的突發精神分裂<br />\n<br />\n情況如同一個媾唔到女既毒撚<br />\n見到人地如膠似漆的憤怒一樣<br />\n<br />\n分析完畢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"22ac401df0b49f30d7d3a7f2f08e71260cd1aa86","tid":334753,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T04:25:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66bb9c1b6e15aaab9d196c49febf0b4050b6649f","tid":334753,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T04:29:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港獌狗仲衰撚過抗日戰爭的支那人<br />\n<br />\nRIO來香港,咪同周秀娜屌西<br />\n你估同你地fans聚會咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好啦,攪次波比你地班死獌狗J下啦<br />\n咪出副選囉,比你地J下班青年軍囉<br />\n<br />\n正選就屌你班女獌狗,仲衰撚過慰安婦<br />\n副選就比你班男獌狗J下<br />\n<br />\n所以做獌狗,真係比起抗日戰爭既支那人都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"3fd542fd1eac9a965ec32c713ea116e98ccba0bd","tid":334753,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T04:30:49.000Z","msg":"女獌比球星享樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n男獌買票入場J下青年軍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa2483738ad5d0ec526f742ecd83a6ebc50fbf09","tid":334753,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T04:38:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7545b2857b5852f2c86ee1f8dbd4a81faac70c51","tid":334753,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T15:33:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}